  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Susume! Taisen Puzzle Dama: Tōkon! Marutama Chō is a puzzle video game released in 1998 on the Nintendo 64 in Japan only. The game was developed and published by Konami. It is a port of the arcade and PlayStation game Susume! Taisen Puzzle-Dama (Let's Attack Crazy Cross), originally released in 1996, but also features characters and gameplay from the spin-off Taisen Tokkae-Dama.",
